            <h2 class="classTitle"><a href="/classDetail">親手製作 - <span>日式布丁草莓蛋糕</span></a></h2>
            <div class="classTime"><i class="fas fa-calendar"></i>2022/03/19 (六）14:00 ~ 16:30 </div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <div class="remain">
              <span>剩餘人數:</span><span id="remainNum">5</span><span>人</span>
