            <div class="classTime"><i class="fas fa-calendar"></i>2022/03/20 (日）10:00 ~ 12:30 </div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <div class="remain">
              <span>剩餘人數:</span><span id="remainNum">5</span><span>人</span>
            </div>
            <div class="classInfo">
              <h3>課程簡介</h3>
              <p class="desc">
                親手製作蛋糕，就算是新手也能一次學會製作技巧！綿密奶油配上新鮮草莓點綴～製作出小熊造型的草莓奶油蛋糕！
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="classCard">
          <div class="classImg">
            <a href="#"> <img src="img/class/cookie-monster.jpeg"></a>
          </div>
